<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:07:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军调查：以色列坦克开火引发爆炸，造成加沙六名士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-tank-fire-caused-blast-which-killed-six-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018c-f265-d206-a1af-f76d80ad0000</link><description>据调查，坦克炮弹无意中引爆了士兵们计划用来拆除哈马斯隧道的炸药。以色列国防军发言人表示，“吸取的教训已经发送给战场上的士兵”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:53:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-tank-fire-caused-blast-which-killed-six-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018c-f265-d206-a1af-f76d80ad0000</guid></item><item><title>前工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾与南非代表团一起出席联合国最高法院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/former-labour-leader-jeremy-corbyn-joins-south-african-delegation-to-uns-top-court/0000018c-f267-d2f9-a3ef-f6774cf30000</link><description>作为巴勒斯坦事业的长期支持者，科尔宾自 2020 年被英国平等监督机构发现反犹太偏见在他领导下激增后被停职以来，就一直受到反犹太主义的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 08:46:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/former-labour-leader-jeremy-corbyn-joins-south-african-delegation-to-uns-top-court/0000018c-f267-d2f9-a3ef-f6774cf30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院禁止本-格维尔在抗议期间向警察发出命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-bars-ben-gvir-from-giving-police-orders-during-protests/0000018c-f24c-d206-a1af-f76ce4a30000</link><description>法院此前曾裁定，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben-Gvir) 不应就抗议者向警方发出命令。 法院临时院长表示，本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben-Gvir) 违反了该裁决</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 07:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-bars-ben-gvir-from-giving-police-orders-during-protests/0000018c-f24c-d206-a1af-f76ce4a30000</guid></item><item><title>在北部边境，以色列未能将战术胜利转化为战略收益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/on-northern-border-israel-fails-to-translate-tactical-victories-into-strategic-gains/0000018c-eff1-d312-addf-eff314b30000</link><description>以色列国防军对真主党的袭击使该组织的精锐拉德万部队稍微远离边境，但该组织仍在设法进行日常袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 04:07:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/on-northern-border-israel-fails-to-translate-tactical-victories-into-strategic-gains/0000018c-eff1-d312-addf-eff314b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；美英在红海击落21架无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-live/blinken-netanyahu-denies-gaza-transfer-as-israeli-policy-idf-probes-six-soldiers-death/0000018c-f15e-d206-a1af-f77ef4de0000</link><description>以色列声称对暗杀真主党无人机部队负责人 ■ 周一，九名以色列国防军士兵在加沙地带丧生 ■ 以色列国防军对造成六名士兵死亡的坦克火灾展开调查 ■ 布林肯在第四次战时访问中会见以色列领导人，表示以色列必须允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部的家园 ■ 布林肯称对以色列的种族灭绝指控“毫无根据”，英国首相卡梅伦表示，他“担心”以色列可能违反了国际法 ■ 以色列外交部否认参与将加沙居民迁出加沙地带的计划</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 03:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-live/blinken-netanyahu-denies-gaza-transfer-as-israeli-policy-idf-probes-six-soldiers-death/0000018c-f15e-d206-a1af-f77ef4de0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党精准先例：使用反坦克导弹狙击以色列住宅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollahs-precision-precedent-sniping-at-israeli-homes-using-antitank-missiles/0000018c-efe2-d312-addf-efe20a870000</link><description>据信真主党是第一个使用精确反坦克导弹瞄准民用建筑的组织。数十座以色列建筑遭到直接袭击——现在甚至连没有撤离的城镇也在射程之内</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 02:33:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollahs-precision-precedent-sniping-at-israeli-homes-using-antitank-missiles/0000018c-efe2-d312-addf-efe20a870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部城市市长致内塔尼亚胡：允许高中生进行枪械训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-southern-israeli-city-to-netanyahu-allow-firearm-training-for-high-schoolers/0000018c-ef2f-d7da-adac-ff3f2eb30000</link><description>加特镇市长阿维拉姆·达哈里 (Aviram Dahari) 写道，该市“希望在以色列人民为家园而战的日子里成为实施这项非常基础的训练的先锋”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:23:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-southern-israeli-city-to-netanyahu-allow-firearm-training-for-high-schoolers/0000018c-ef2f-d7da-adac-ff3f2eb30000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：针对以色列的种族灭绝指控“毫无根据”；必须允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/blinken-genocide-charge-against-israel-meritless-palestinians-must-be-allowed-return/0000018c-ef8f-da6b-abdd-ffcf48d60000</link><description>布林肯在周二与以色列官员会面后的新闻发布会上发表了讲话。与此同时，美国和以色列在加沙的未来问题上仍存在严重分歧 — — 特别是关于重振巴勒斯坦权力机构的潜在作用，布林肯将于周三会见该权力机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/blinken-genocide-charge-against-israel-meritless-palestinians-must-be-allowed-return/0000018c-ef8f-da6b-abdd-ffcf48d60000</guid></item><item><title>“当我们无法同情巴勒斯坦人时，我们怎么能指望其他人同情我们呢？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-09/ty-article-podcast/.premium/how-can-we-expect-others-to-empathize-with-us-if-we-fail-to-empathize-with-palestinians/0000018c-ef0a-d7da-adac-ff1b816a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 17:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-09/ty-article-podcast/.premium/how-can-we-expect-others-to-empathize-with-us-if-we-fail-to-empathize-with-palestinians/0000018c-ef0a-d7da-adac-ff1b816a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属试图阻止对加沙的援助，在布林肯面前示威</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-attempt-to-block-aid-into-gaza-protest-in-front-of-blinken/0000018c-eea8-d7da-adac-feb940080000</link><description>“我们的政府没有履行其使命。我们需要美国的紧急帮助，我们需要人质现在活着回家。我们为什么现在在这里？我们的亲人被关押在加沙 100 天后，”拥有美国和以色列双重国籍的齐皮·海托夫斯基 (Tsipi Haitovski) 在抗议活动中说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 16:07:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-attempt-to-block-aid-into-gaza-protest-in-front-of-blinken/0000018c-eea8-d7da-adac-feb940080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列声称在数十次跨境袭击中杀死了真主党无人机负责人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hezbollah-exchange-dozens-of-cross-border-strikes-on-tuesday/0000018c-ee36-d7da-adac-fe375bbb0000</link><description>真主党从黎巴嫩向以色列国防军基地发射爆炸性无人机，而以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击导致三名真主党战士死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 15:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hezbollah-exchange-dozens-of-cross-border-strikes-on-tuesday/0000018c-ee36-d7da-adac-fe375bbb0000</guid></item><item><title>接地：以色列人目前不属于世界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</link><description>特拉维夫的本古里安国际机场空无一人，外国航空公司没有航班飞往这里，以色列人只是梦想着度假</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</guid></item><item><title>“当以色列与哈马斯战争爆发时，Apple TV 要求停止编写剧本”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-01-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-the-israel-hamas-war-broke-out-apple-tv-asked-to-stop-writing-the-script/0000018c-ee37-d7da-adac-fe37d7080000<