Jan 2024 12:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/released-israeli-hostage-to-knesset-i-saw-them-harming-women-in-captivity/0000018c-edd3-d0b4-a7ce-fff308f50000</guid></item><item><title>70名以色列议员签署动议，驱逐支持国际法院种族灭绝指控的MK</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/70-israeli-lawmakers-sign-motion-to-expel-mk-for-supporting-icj-genocide-charges/0000018c-ed46-d7fa-a9be-fd67f72f0000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫议员表示，“虽然那些明确呼吁用火或原子弹摧毁加沙的人坐在内阁会议桌前，但我面临着因‘支持针对以色列的武装斗争’未经证实的指控而被驱逐”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 10:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/70-israeli-lawmakers-sign-motion-to-expel-mk-for-supporting-icj-genocide-charges/0000018c-ed46-d7fa-a9be-fd67f72f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周一在加沙战斗中丧生的九名以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-ed4a-d7fa-a9be-fd6fa5960000</link><description>被杀的士兵是加夫里尔·布鲁姆（Gavriel Bloom），27 岁；大卫·施瓦茨，26；亚基尔·赫克斯特，26 岁；罗伊塔尔，19 岁；罗伊·亚伯拉罕·迈蒙，24 岁；阿齐瓦·亚辛斯基，35 岁；阿米特·摩西·沙哈尔，25 岁​​；丹尼斯·克罗赫马洛夫·韦克斯勒，32 岁；罗恩·埃弗里米，26 岁</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 09:29:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-ed4a-d7fa-a9be-fd6fa5960000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列男子在以色列北部的家中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-fatally-shot-in-his-home-in-northern-israel/0000018c-ed23-db55-a39e-ffb719040000</link><description>受害者没有犯罪记录，是以色列阿拉伯社区自 2024 年初以来的第三名凶杀案受害者。警方怀疑枪击动机与他在灰色市场获得的一笔贷款有关</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 08:01:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-fatally-shot-in-his-home-in-northern-israel/0000018c-ed23-db55-a39e-ffb719040000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯提醒以色列，加沙战争尚未结束，北方紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reminds-israel-that-the-gaza-war-is-not-over-as-tensions-rise-in-the-north/0000018c-eb05-d0e9-a3de-ffcd85040000</link><description>以色列用英语和希伯来语窃窃私语，加沙战争的第三阶段已经开始——从大规模空中和地面战斗转向有针对性的行动 ■ 拉德万部队负责人被暗杀是向真主党高级官员发出的信息■ 布林肯来这里是为了推动加沙和黎巴嫩的解决方案，但他在耶路撒冷的东道主对此表示怀疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reminds-israel-that-the-gaza-war-is-not-over-as-tensions-rise-in-the-north/0000018c-eb05-d0e9-a3de-ffcd85040000</guid></item></channel></rss>